description: Try our easy to follow Coconut Orange Bunny Ear Cake recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Coconut Orange Bunny Ear Cake Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 1.75 cup White Wings Self Raising Flour
100 g Cadbury Baking Chocolate Chips White
250 g CSR Buttercream Icing Mix Vanilla

recipeInstructions.text: Top with second cake and use remaining icing to cover the two cakes. Sprinkle with shredded coconut. 1Gently press the ears into the top of the cake and use liquorice and marshmallow for facial features.
